column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid, p.ra, p.dec,  p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  s.specobjid, s.class,s.z as redshift,  ga.bptclass, ga.oh_p5#, ga.lgm_tot_p5#, ga.lgm_fib_p5#,  ga.sfr_tot_p5#, sfr_fib_p5#, specsfr_tot_p5# FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS ga ON ga.specObjID = p.objid WHERE  s.z BETWEEN # AND #   AND s.class = &&&
